    }
  ],
  "inter_chunk_silence_ms": 650,
  "chunks": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "text": "Gemini CLI just shipped its biggest update yet.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d4e25ca5fc0c224c3e0ab76fd6a9566781547836866f42649a0d6a59b77526da",
      "wav": "chunk-00.wav",
      "duration": 2.9257142857142857,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 0
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "text": "Version 0.40 brings local Gemma support straight to your terminal.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b703301480abba84723a6fd6f2b55ef76c68e1ed925192deea7655f7374dcace",
      "wav": "chunk-01.wav",
      "duration": 4.040272108843538,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 8
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "The Google Gemma team confirmed it on launch day.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0b1e21a76f3fc18386034ba28fe0d2b88b036fda4b47790eef708ffaa4f3e6a3",
      "wav": "chunk-02.wav",
      "duration": 2.5541950113378684,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 18
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "Over 150 improvements landed in this single release.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a149b669f7f1d98ab6d643cd4a952632cda5a2ada8b9cfce98a2bc3c27a979db",
      "wav": "chunk-03.wav",
      "duration": 3.2043537414965986,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 27
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "Security, memory, and a streamlined UI got serious upgrades.",
      "checksum": "sha256:7ff5f26e117bee22ea43f5a8feb24057c97702716cedfcf72480c4c44819d466",
      "wav": "chunk-04.wav",
      "duration": 3.7616326530612243,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 35
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "And the roadmap says full local model execution is coming next.",
      "checksum": "sha256:06d0e465315c5fcaaf656ddcbeb9f3528812fd1a3987337feaedd02fe97e87ec",
      "wav": "chunk-05.wav",
      "duration": 3.436553287981859,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 44
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "Local Gemma is experimental but already works.",
      "checksum": "sha256:eac52bb5f724e11db759219576816dcc91dad91732190bd25b548b4a945015e9",
      "wav": "chunk-06.wav",
      "duration": 2.7399546485260773,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 55
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "You set it up with the gemini gemma setup command.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ce7f52538bc0f0e4186887d44cf823e1e880060e2e010c07b7bacde2304efc83",
      "wav": "chunk-07.wav",
      "duration": 3.0650340136054424,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 62
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "text": "The CLI downloads the LiteRT runtime and a 1 gigabyte Gemma 3 model.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9c2fa85df615ff5ea4dbb1dbd8ebca8fe842e2842128ea0c31759634aac38101",
      "wav": "chunk-08.wav",
      "duration": 3.9938321995464854,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 72
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "text": "You accept the Gemma terms of use and the install runs locally.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b40bacf3883e64ab1035a30e71d1fea08abfebaf23dff8232c9e426a0f6e6f9d",
      "wav": "chunk-09.wav",
      "duration": 3.436553287981859,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 85
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "text": "Then you check status with the slash gemma command.",
      "checksum": "sha256:471737b71ed11df7f338845c90772df11c10844b9a4d1aa0049dd5c3e5940620",
      "wav": "chunk-10.wav",
      "duration": 2.7399546485260773,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 97
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "text": "To turn the router on, open slash settings and flip the Enable Gemma Model Router toggle.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9bb09ba0bc5abcf1b0e07b80636609ba6e08e5d081524463d03e8928344ce664",
      "wav": "chunk-11.wav",
      "duration": 4.690430839002268,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 106
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "text": "Or set experimental dot gemma to true in your settings dot json file.",
      "checksum": "sha256:2fda6fe685e5e233a35ae8cf29657f4f20c3def8513845359d889a128ad9cdda",
      "wav": "chunk-12.wav",
      "duration": 4.040272108843538,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 122
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "text": "So what is Gemma actually doing here? Gemma 3 is a 1 billion parameter model with a GPU-accelerated build.",
      "checksum": "sha256:65f965864dce0287af4f98225a1ed7242712b91a970a6a62a080f37349b12729",
      "wav": "chunk-13.wav",
      "duration": 6.733786848072563,
      "word_count": 19,
      "words_offset": 135
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "text": "It runs on your hardware through the LiteRT-LM runtime.",
      "checksum": "sha256:2f26f8baf51b2eaa9b7bc92a302c397b6c9907e62c03e6b0354acdcff16c826b",
      "wav": "chunk-14.wav",
      "duration": 2.9257142857142857,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 154
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "text": "Today it powers intelligent model routing.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b2584127139dbdd4a902322b7ff7f6e76e2512cfa7c5c6b5f560ceeb3acf93f5",
      "wav": "chunk-15.wav",
      "duration": 2.2755555555555556,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 163
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "text": "It decides which model handles each prompt, locally.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ec852236bbd8aa55881e89a1c3e16c6e8aacd15f7cba308a9e098b9867fd59e3",
      "wav": "chunk-16.wav",
      "duration": 2.8328344671201813,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 169
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "text": "Full local model execution is next on the roadmap.",
      "checksum": "sha256:dad9bce17242cac4d58b53af553650a2d8feddb04f2969530a52fc5cf61e76d7",
      "wav": "chunk-17.wav",
      "duration": 2.8792743764172335,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 177
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "text": "Gemma 3 is the foothold. Beyond Gemma, five upgrades stand out.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3abf6d7fa24bdb518476ee91cca3b5aa66e49ca09a263fb5e1c4ef64bc43ffe9",
      "wav": "chunk-18.wav",
      "duration": 4.31891156462585,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 186
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "text": "Tiered memory now stores context across four distinct layers.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c9427b89f8a2ad27f72ff0f50bb9a4c4aaf28c13eceba0816d31d0dcb17044da",
      "wav": "chunk-19.wav",
      "duration": 3.622312925170068,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 197
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "text": "Project rules live in a GEMINI dot md file at your repo root.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d51a7678eaba8f6ade3b4690ba2e3f09a1f57a234977ad13be0521cad16b9e7a",
      "wav": "chunk-20.wav",
      "duration": 3.7616326530612243,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 206
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "text": "Subdirectory rules scope down to specific folders.",
      "checksum": "sha256:4c693f85f25f73a0f677e4e5644d1b866783b7f769fcc0a68dd0a3521e73c19f",
      "wav": "chunk-21.wav",
      "duration": 2.8328344671201813,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 219
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "text": "Private memory stays local and never commits to the repo.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8538286ce372131698c545567fa7ce853f2b4c6b7b5062badf3f850b7a6762df",
      "wav": "chunk-22.wav",
      "duration": 3.111473922902494,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 226
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "text": "Global memory follows you across every workspace you open.",
      "checksum": "sha256:207e19af84d4fccb903343136337164169ceb6f2dcda0329c62bf7010fef54b7",
      "wav": "chunk-23.wav",
      "duration": 3.0650340136054424,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 236
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "text": "Auto memory extracts reusable skills from your old sessions automatically.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e19826cbcda8dadc4f1bda573b136172e18d6a6039dc1538b04bf08a286d47ca",
      "wav": "chunk-24.wav",
      "duration": 4.133151927437642,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 245
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "text": "The background agent drafts new SKILL dot md files from idle conversations.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a2ea8d6384c080b79b457296e359fb787e4cddad94386eab9a86de64ac2851e1",
      "wav": "chunk-25.wav",
      "duration": 4.6439909297052155,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 255
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "text": "Run slash memory inbox to review and promote what it finds.",
      "checksum": "sha256:cdbd65d9e1a5c66ba0745399f312af8b7003072177f393e901c836bbe6e5152b",
      "wav": "chunk-26.wav",
      "duration": 3.250793650793651,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 267
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "text": "Compact tool output replaces noisy tool-call boxes with a clean structured format.",
      "checksum": "sha256:023539e6309656cf3ff3d10e2a706ee2eebc6b518f98be01baec35cd4aaf7c45",
      "wav": "chunk-27.wav",
      "duration": 4.551111111111111,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 278
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "text": "File reads, searches, and directory lists all render cleanly now.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f2c708688ae8aa15efab38f7d6a0be03a9d7f1d145fd30ba57a485bcab2b9562",
      "wav": "chunk-28.wav",
      "duration": 3.5294331065759637,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 290
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "text": "Topic narrations replace agent chatter with descriptive section headers across every agent.",
      "checksum": "sha256:52860dfa086510b4a254ffa8d7250e4403473a39e520d4eafa4523e94012f07e",
      "wav": "chunk-29.wav",
      "duration": 4.876190476190477,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 300
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "text": "And the task tracker keeps a persistent objective list while the agent works through complex goals.",
      "checksum": "sha256:31908ba98f7ce6f72b8ceeee3d062eeda94df1d1a6b0f1b7ef177b7776e0684e",
      "wav": "chunk-30.wav",
      "duration": 5.479909297052155,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 312
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "text": "Performance and security got serious upgrades too.",
      "checksum": "sha256:717a2d3c9c5195017bfb66ea28608d261c9fa07abfeee0684add12ace27fc843",
      "wav": "chunk-31.wav",
      "duration": 2.8792743764172335,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 328
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "text": "Ripgrep is now bundled into the CLI for lightning-fast offline search.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ab720fabde1a1033fffe24ea9c509bab549baf902141195df0efab530620368d",
      "wav": "chunk-32.wav",
      "duration": 3.947392290249433,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 335
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "text": "Memory usage dropped significantly for DevTools and large output streams.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d658406c7c2d98d757e23a8a1941a7d30817b403c1dd73fd1f2a9314b2159cd8",
      "wav": "chunk-33.wav",
      "duration": 3.6687528344671203,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 346
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "text": "Sandboxing improved for Docker and macOS Seatbelt environments.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ff84fe3445cf87b7de78eabc5f8979f252153fd9200430e46ac56729ab7c33f9",
      "wav": "chunk-34.wav",
      "duration": 3.250793650793651,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 356
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "text": "Shell command validation blocks injection attacks before they execute.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9d29400edf083b1d5f53a706bb29ae100dfcb8d5c2d2c653555d7fdf81c5f984",
      "wav": "chunk-35.wav",
      "duration": 3.6687528344671203,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 364
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "text": "The slash new command starts a fresh session instantly.",
      "checksum": "sha256:cfd6a370ded23b3e8944b7789d106523266b073ea5c7549099047eea62ad6156",
      "wav": "chunk-36.wav",
      "duration": 2.7399546485260773,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 373
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "text": "New colorblind-friendly themes ship out of the box.",
      "checksum": "sha256:5956b6559c2d669e44dcdc5e889bbbc008a1a6f3a61e1ab1b3180298985fa6b2",
      "wav": "chunk-37.wav",
      "duration": 3.01859410430839,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 382
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "text": "This is the local agent shift. Update Gemini CLI today and try Gemma yourself.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a1392a456d33e068711d50fc5367cff675263c57dbb49b21ce1f3f58de9af2b8",
      "wav": "chunk-38.wav",
      "duration": 4.6439909297052155,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 390
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "text": "Tried Gemini CLI already, or sticking with Claude Code or Codex?",
      "checksum": "sha256:168a10475ce0ca865884e8296247a51d14669d32435f56146171418dd646295a",
      "wav": "chunk-39.wav",
      "duration": 3.6687528344671203,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 404
    }
  ]
}